	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think it's more of a case that, if your art is bad, it'll be more obvious on the SNES than it is on the NES. The technique <em>is</em> different because you need to focus on different things, but I don't think it's any harder or easier to get something to look good on either console.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


