	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Isometric and oblique 45 look really cool, but are much harder to pull off on the NES, because of all the overlaps. If you end up deciding on one of these, I guess oblique 45 is more fitting.<br /><br />The other 2 look more like your typical NES game. A side view is very limited in terms of interaction with the environment, so oblique 90 would probably be the next best choice IMO.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


